config SENSOR_NODE
	bool "Custom Sensor Node UART driver"
	default y
	depends on SENSOR && UART_INTERRUPT_DRIVEN
	help
	  Enable the custom sensor driver that receives data from
	  the Home Security Sensor Node over UART. The driver implements
	  the standard Zephyr Sensor API (fetch / channel_get).
